 - map files (cd map; make all)
 - man pages (cd bin; make all)
 - update web site (cd pyx12/htdocs/; svn export --force https://pyx12.svn.sourceforge.net/svnroot/pyx12/pyx12-web/trunk/ .)

make packages
 - python setup.py sdist --force-manifest
